Dark Chocolate Market - Competitive and Segmentation Analysis:

**Segments**

- Based on type, the global dark chocolate market can be segmented into organic dark chocolate, inorganic dark chocolate.
- On the basis of distribution channel, the market is categorized into supermarket/hypermarket, convenience stores, online retail.
- By product type, the market can be divided into dark chocolate bars, dark chocolate chips, dark chocolate coating.

